==Japanese==
===Noun===
'''一つ''' ([[ひとつ]], ''hitotsu)

# [[one]] thing [small or without a counter category]
#: 一つ (ひとつ, ''hitotsu) is only used when the item counted has no specific counter category. See [[w:Japanese counter word|Wikipedia's "Japanese counter word" entry]] for details.

